&&9\cdot\frac{1}{f^{4}}
\sum_{j_1j_2j_3=1}^{2l}\sum_{m_1m_2m_3}(1-(-1)^{j_1+j_2+j_3})
\frac{(2j_1+1)(2j_2+1)(2j_3+1)}{j_2(j_2+1)j_3(j_3+1)}\;\nonumber \\
&&\times
\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
j_1&j_2&j_3\\
m_1&m_2&m_3
\end{array}\right)^2
\left\{\begin{array}{ccc}
j_1&j_2&j_3\\
l&l&l
\end{array}\right\}^2\nonumber \\
&&+9\cdot\frac{1}{f^{4}}
\sum_{j_1j_2j_3=1}^{2l}\sum_{m_1m_2m_3}(1-(-1)^{j_1+j_2+j_3})
\frac{(2j_1+1)(2j_2+1)(2j_3+1)}{j_1(j_1+1)j_2(j_2+1)j_3(j_3+1)}
\left\{\begin{array}{ccc}
j_1&j_2&j_3\\
l&l&l
\end{array}\right\}^2\nonumber \\
&&\times \Bigg[
-\frac{1}{2}\sqrt{(j_1-m_1)(j_1+m_1+1)(j_2+m_2)(j_2-m_2+1)}\nonumber \\
&&\times
\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
j_1&j_2&j_3\\
m_1+1&m_2&m_3
\end{array}\right)
\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
j_2&j_1&j_3\\
-m_2-1&-m_1&-m_3
\end{array}\right)\nonumber \\
&&-\frac{1}{2}\sqrt{(j_1+m_1)(j_1-m_1+1)(j_2-m_2)(j_2+m_2+1)}\nonumber \\
&&\times
\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
j_1&j_2&j_3\\
m_1-1&m_2&m_3
\end{array}\right)
\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
j_2&j_1&j_3\\
-m_2+1&-m_1&-m_3
\end{array}\right)\nonumber \\
&&-m_1m_2
\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
j_1&j_2&j_3\\
m_1&m_2&m_3
\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
j_2&j_1&j_3\\
-m_2&-m_1&-m_3
\end{array}\right)\Bigg] .

\begin{eqnarray}
C_{+}(j_1 \enspace \pm {1 \over 2} \enspace  \pm{1 \over 2} \enspace m )
&=&
-C_{-}(j_1 \enspace \mp {1 \over 2} \enspace  \mp{1 \over 2} \enspace m )
=
{j_1 \pm m + {1 \over 2} \over 2 j_1 +1}, \nonumber \\
C_{-}(j_1 \enspace \pm {1 \over 2} \enspace \mp{1 \over 2} \enspace m)
&=&
-{\sqrt{(j_1 -m + {1 \over 2})(j_1+ m + {1 \over 2})} \over 2 j_1 +1}, \nonumber \\
C_{+}(j_1 \enspace \pm {1 \over 2} \enspace \mp{1 \over 2} \enspace m)
&=&
{\sqrt{(j_1 -m + {1 \over 2})(j_1+ m + {1 \over 2})} \over 2 j_1 +1}.
\

\begin{eqnarray}
&&{1 \over 2!} \Big\langle
 (-S_{1}^\psi) (-S_{1}^\psi )\Big\rangle_{\mbox{2loop-1PI}}\nonumber \\
&=&
{1 \over f^4}
\sum_{j_1 j_2 j_3} \sum_{m_1 m_2 m_3}\nonumber \\
&&
\left(
4\cdot (7-3){\mbox{Tr}\{(Y_{j_1 m_1} [Y_{j_2 m_2},Y_{j_3 m_3}])^2\} \over
j_1(j_1+1) j_2(j_2+1) j_3(j_3+1)} \right.
\nonumber \\
& &
+4\cdot (7+1){(-1)^{m_1+m_2+m_3} \over j_1 (j_1+1) j_2 (j_2+1) j_3(j_3+1)}
\nonumber \\
&&\times \left.\mbox{Tr} [p_\mu, Y_{j_1m_1}][Y_{j_2m_2},Y_{j_3m_3}]
\mbox{Tr} [p_\mu,
Y_{j_2,-m_2}][Y_{j_1,-m_1},Y_{j_3,-m_3}]
\right)
\nonumber \\ &=&
{32 \over f^4} \left[ F_3^p\left(l\right) - F_3^{np}\left(l\right)
- 2 F_2^p\left(l\right) + 2 F_2^{np}\left(l\right)\right] .
\
